{"tid":269390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔想執著","createTime":"2017-06-03T17:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T02:33:33.000Z","uid":21746,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16746ee0d926b27f8b7c6eec78172887e52fb1cc","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"每次唔開心都叫自己唔好執著 因為執著 所以痛苦<br />\n但真係好難 嗰刻會覺得自己好廢 但又好矛盾 一段關係本質上就係執著嘅根源<br />\n<br />\n諗起如風嘅歌詞<br />\n「或世事統統不過是場夢」夢係虛假嘅 或者世事都係 感情上嘅瓜葛都係<br />\n「但我不過是人非夢」但我係有七情六慾嘅人 會因為世事而傷心 呢啲感覺確實存在<br />\n好矛盾 咁講法我哋係咪對虛假嘅世事太過認真？<br />\n<br />\n冇計 我始終選擇去愛一個人 但當中又會有苦有甜<br />\n我又應該點樣面對？我係咪選擇左去執著呢？我唔執著 又係咪唔認真對待感情呢？好明顯呢啲問題都顯示到我嘅執著<br />\n<br />\n可能認認真真放低執著 係要好似和尚尼姑咁出家"},{"pid":"d69aa15a82fd1b9523c649fc8442eee11042f21b","tid":269390,"uid":100626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"睇淡啲段感情 唔好毫無保留咁愛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9915c4866085c3597441fdba4d66536c5a97a3e","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇淡啲段感情 唔好毫無保留咁愛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者我太敏感 觀察力又太強 可能旁人眼中係件細微嘅事 但我好似get到啲複雜嘅messages<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848d1ebec841fc1b46230fdd3a6caaf15059aabf","tid":269390,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"識input 就要識output<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你0 input<br />\n<br />\n自己參透下"},{"pid":"1611769d5334634b35aa5a9c8a59cf3899d55964","tid":269390,"uid":69791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"612296a32510759a795721928a75f74f0505be16","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識input 就要識output<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你0 input<br />\n<br />\n自己參透下</blockquote><br />\n明嘅"},{"pid":"0fbd01fd45556880d8ead72d33626e9cc6c97e4b","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>EXAC7LY<br />\n庸人自擾</blockquote><br />\n其實我知佢有mon post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bea980b23af302f9b72d902f7e9639603ebb1e4","tid":269390,"uid":79983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"同你好似 好辛苦 每晚一靜落黎就亂諗野 我知有啲野唔應該執著但我控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1e22be7364e8a3aebbdfa0cb3c308694f39e72","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你好似 好辛苦 每晚一靜落黎就亂諗野 我知有啲野唔應該執著但我控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日發生左小小事 其實我真係好難同佢講清楚我嬲乜 因為佢聽完8成機會覺得我唔識體諒佢 唉"},{"pid":"2513fbddec795a720651a8933ce8412f10f1a2f6","tid":269390,"uid":79983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:38:50.000Z","msg":"咪以為係到亂發脾氣但唔在意你 邊會咁樣呀 不過你都係直接同佢講好啲 廢事有乜誤會啦"},{"pid":"ff1a4f8a9fa3f1a7465960b08e771a99ca196eab","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪以為係到亂發脾氣但唔在意你 邊會咁樣呀 不過你都係直接同佢講好啲 廢事有乜誤會啦</blockquote><br />\n因為關埋其他人事所以廢事嘈 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d662e559315a89d8759a976c795fd0254efdc78c","tid":269390,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:57:00.000Z","msg":"I know that feel sis<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f393747e2f5a121516f7a8a1b5993de2af30d51d","tid":269390,"uid":63142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:32:57.000Z","msg":"以前每次同你講我因為見到你地一齊玩而唔開心，你就只係成日話我諗多左，諗埋一邊。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2610d9add769ee0c4428d0b260ebb7d208ff20","tid":269390,"uid":63142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:34:33.000Z","msg":"執著唔係件好事，但真係控制唔到"},{"pid":"9282b6a58862c888c1a09847500492aa51b8a4d2","tid":269390,"uid":67096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:36:51.000Z","msg":"點解見到你關心其他人 我個心咁痛 唔係同自己講好左 要放低啦咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42441b58a8fec5457a8240ac77a33b707e4ea4b9","tid":269390,"uid":21746,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"如果你睇緊呢個post 希望你知道<br />\n有啲嘢我肯接受 係因為人情<br />\n但假如我唔肯接受 係因為道理<br />\n或者我真係嬲緊自己唔夠大方同隨和<br />\nSorry<br />\n我愛你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}